In the previous live examples, try using visibility: hidden or display: none instead of visibility: collapse Using visibility: hidden, the item is made invisible, but the box is kept in the formatting structure, so it still behaves as if it were part of the layout When you use display: none, the item is completely removed from the formatting structure Not only is it invisible but the structure is removed as well This means counters ignore it and things like transitions do not run Help improve MDN
